      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains exceptionally composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and recently refreshed bushings. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a full VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustments to ensure the high-revving powerplant operates within factory tolerances. While the exterior displays minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical vitals are superlative, featuring a healthy factory variable M differential and a linear, communicative steering rack. A robust driver\u2019s specimen with a clean underside and no structural fatigue.",
